    <item>
      <title>戴比尔斯大幅降价，放弃钻石战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/de-beers-capitulates-on-diamond-strategy-with-big-price-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为全球最大的钻石生产商，戴比尔斯已全线下调钻石价格 10% 以上，放弃为低迷的市场寻找支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/de-beers-capitulates-on-diamond-strategy-with-big-price-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 10:27:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车工人因削减德国成本计划开始罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工会领袖与管理层在如何削减大众汽车同名品牌的成本问题上陷入僵局，德国各地的大众汽车工人于周一发起罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞再次向巴尼耶施压，法国债券表现落后于其他债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党再次威胁，如果 2025 年预算要求得不到满足，她将推翻法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶领导的政府。此后，法国债券和股票再度承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管马科斯努力平息纷争，杜特尔特仍面临弹劾案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/impeachment-case-filed-against-philippines-vp-sara-duterte</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾民间团体周一对副总统萨拉·杜特尔特提起弹劾诉讼，但此举在明年中期选举前可能难以获得议员支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/impeachment-case-filed-against-philippines-vp-sara-duterte</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦民众称欧洲央行将讨论进一步降息但不确定性较高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行下周很可能再次降息，尽管政策制定者将讨论比平时更大幅度的举措，但他们应该谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比跌至历史新低，债券在经济增长放缓后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rupee-falls-to-new-record-low-bonds-gain-after-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示经济增长大幅放缓，印度卢比跌至历史新低。市场押注央行可能比预期更早降息，债券价格延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rupee-falls-to-new-record-low-bonds-gain-after-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强导致黄金下跌，焦点转向美国就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/gold-slips-as-trump-s-brics-currency-warning-boosts-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强，金价下跌，投资者关注周五公布的美国关键数据，这些数据可能为美联储本月晚些时候的利率决定提供线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/gold-slips-as-trump-s-brics-currency-warning-boosts-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 01:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
